<Schematic Name="CD4066 buffer bypass" Description="CMOS soft-switching bypass: input buffer (JFET) feeds two CD4066 switch elements driven by complementary control signals from an SPST footswitch + CD4013-style latch. Audio biased to Vref (4.5V) for linear CMOS operation. Reference topology per beavisaudio.com/techpages/buffers and freestompboxes.org discussions." PartNumber="">
